Who knew I'd get to see
Lee Jae-hyeong in real life?

317
00:19:42,098 --> 00:19:43,558
Don't you know who he is?

318
00:19:43,641 --> 00:19:44,976
Holy cow.

319
00:19:45,059 --> 00:19:47,186
He played in the majors
for the New York Hartz!

320
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,688
Oh, come on.

321
00:19:48,771 --> 00:19:50,481
Of course, I know who he is!

322
00:19:50,565 --> 00:19:53,401
How could I not know Mr. Lee Jae-hyeong?

323
