Well, I'm just a corporate worker now.

324
00:19:58,489 --> 00:20:00,909
My goodness, just a coporate worker?

325
00:20:00,992 --> 00:20:03,328
You're the president of Sports Eunseong.

326
00:20:03,411 --> 00:20:05,622
-Right, Ms. Wi?
-Yes.

327
00:20:05,705 --> 00:20:07,415
