359
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:09,328
Hey, bro.

360
00:22:10,788 --> 00:22:13,374
We're watching the game
after the first pitch, right?

361
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:16,419
Come on, they gave us VIP seats!

362
00:22:16,502 --> 00:22:19,464
