366
00:22:27,055 --> 00:22:29,223
Why are you in a bad mood? What happened?

367
00:22:29,766 --> 00:22:30,933
Can I get an autograph?

368
00:22:31,517 --> 00:22:32,518
What a pretty name.

369
00:22:35,021 --> 00:22:36,230
No, but really,

370
00:22:36,314 --> 00:22:39,484
my daughter is a huge fan
of Mr. Lee Jae-hyeong.

371
00:22:39,567 --> 00:22:41,527
You retired too early.

372
00:22:43,905 --> 00:22:44,947
Jeez.

373
00:22:45,615 --> 00:22:48,951
I wondered where I'd seen him before.

374
00:22:51,746 --> 00:22:53,790
So you used to be a baseball player?

375
00:22:57,293 --> 00:23:00,254
I played in the pros for a bit.

376
00:23:02,423 --> 00:23:04,008
I was pretty famous, you know.

377
00:23:04,592 --> 00:23:06,135
Could you show some more interest?

378
00:23:12,141 --> 00:23:14,018
What should we have for dinner later?

379
00:23:14,852 --> 00:23:16,062
