without watching the game?

464
00:30:14,271 --> 00:30:15,856
You have Ms. Wi's number, right?

465
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,900
Yeah, I think I got her business card.

466
00:30:17,983 --> 00:30:18,859
Give it to me.

467
00:30:19,652 --> 00:30:20,736
Why?

468
00:30:20,819 --> 00:30:22,238
Because the interview went badly?

469
00:30:22,821 --> 00:30:26,283
No, it's because
I said something I shouldn't have.

470
00:30:26,909 --> 00:30:28,327
What did you say?

471
00:30:28,410 --> 00:30:31,247
Did you think
I was one of the hostesses there?

472
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:32,289
Jeez.

473
00:30:32,373 --> 00:30:34,542
Are you saying you were dressed like that

474
00:30:34,625 --> 00:30:37,878
to do some undercover reporting
or something like that?

475
00:30:40,548 --> 00:30:42,174
What if I was?

476
00:30:43,259 --> 00:30:44,760
Bro, have you lost your mind?

477
00:30:44,843 --> 00:30:47,638
Even if you had suspicions,
you should've kept them to yourself.

478
00:30:47,721 --> 00:30:50,182
Why would you say that to her face?

479
00:30:51,433 --> 00:30:52,351
Do you think

480
00:30:53,811 --> 00:30:54,770
she got really offended?

481
00:30:55,354 --> 00:30:57,189
Totally.

482
00:30:57,982 --> 00:31:00,067
I would've sued you immediately.

483
00:31:00,150 --> 00:31:01,026
Come on.

484
00:31:02,152 --> 00:31:03,112
Was it that bad?

485
00:31:03,195 --> 00:31:05,030
Totally.

486
00:31:11,787 --> 00:31:15,708
Jeez, I'll lose face if I call her first.

487
00:31:17,668 --> 00:31:18,627
All right.

488
00:31:19,378 --> 00:31:20,963
I'll save her number first.

489
00:31:21,964 --> 00:31:23,215
Wait a minute.

490
00:31:23,299 --> 00:31:26,260
If I save her number,
she'll see my name when I message her.

491
00:31:27,177 --> 00:31:28,137
Darn it.

492
00:31:30,014 --> 00:31:31,015
Goodness.

493
00:31:31,098 --> 00:31:32,808
-Hello.
-Hello.

494
00:31:32,891 --> 00:31:34,226
I saw you throw the first pitch.

495
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,228
You looked amazing.

496
00:31:36,312 --> 00:31:37,313
