-By the way,

497
00:31:37,396 --> 00:31:40,232
I heard your mother is
actress Seong Ae-suk.

498
00:31:40,316 --> 00:31:43,068
You must've gotten
your acting genes from her.

499
00:31:47,406 --> 00:31:49,742
-Please go ahead. I have a call to make.
-Come on.

500
00:31:49,825 --> 00:31:51,285
-Let's go up together.
