501
00:31:52,161 --> 00:31:52,995
Go ahead.

502
00:31:59,293 --> 00:32:01,670
-It says your mother is Seong Ae-suk,
-Did you plan on revealing that your…

503
00:32:01,754 --> 00:32:03,047
